      "content": "Mojang's Yggdrasil session server (sessionserver.mojang.com) used in the Minecraft Java Edition login handshake. Exposes the canonical skin and cape texture lookup keyed by UUID, the client-side /join and server-side /hasJoined verification calls, and the SHA-1 blocked-server hash list.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Mojang Studios",
